sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM Servers
    participant Prom as Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS
    participant SatEng as Saturation Engine
    participant Cache as Decision Cache<br/>(In-Memory)
    participant VACtrl as VariantAutoscaling<br/>Controller
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Metrics as WVA Metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HPA as HPA / KEDA

    Note over vLLM,HPA: Flow 1: Saturation-Based Autoscaling Loop

    vLLM->>Prom: Expose KV cache & queue metrics
    SatEng->>Prom: PromQL query (HTTPS/9091)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA token)<br/>TLS: service CA cert
    Prom-->>SatEng: KV cache utilization, queue depth
    SatEng->>SatEng: Compute desired replicas<br/>(Kalman filter smoothing)
    SatEng->>Cache: Store scaling decision
    Cache->>VACtrl: Trigger reconcile (channel)
    VACtrl->>K8s: Update VariantAutoscaling CR status<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS
    SatEng->>Metrics: Emit wva_desired_replicas,<br/>wva_current_replicas, wva_desired_ratio
    Prom->>Metrics: Scrape /metrics (HTTPS/8443)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    HPA->>Prom: Query wva_desired_replicas<br/>(HTTPS/9091)
    HPA->>K8s: Scale Deployment replicas

    Note over vLLM,HPA: Flow 2: Scale-from-Zero via InferencePool

    participant IPCtrl as InferencePool<br/>Controller
    participant DS as Datastore<br/>(In-Memory)
    participant SFZ as Scale-from-Zero<br/>Engine

    IPCtrl->>K8s: Watch InferencePool CRs<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS
    K8s-->>IPCtrl: InferencePool events
    IPCtrl->>DS: Sync endpoint data
    SFZ->>DS: Check endpoint pools
    SFZ->>K8s: Scale deployment (scale subresource)<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS

    Note over vLLM,HPA: Flow 3: ConfigMap-Driven Configuration

    participant CMCtrl as ConfigMap<br/>Controller

    CMCtrl->>K8s: Watch ConfigMaps<br/>Auth: SA Token, TLS
    K8s-->>CMCtrl: ConfigMap change events
    CMCtrl->>CMCtrl: Update config store (in-memory)
